25/* Before including this file, some macros must be defined:
26 BDESC (mask, icode, name, code, comparison, flag)
27 -- definition of each builtin
28 BDESC_FIRST (kind, KIND, mask, icode, name, code, comparison, flag)
29 -- like BDESC, but used for the first builtin in each category;
30 bdesc_##kind will be used in the name of the array and
31 IX86_BUILTIN__BDESC_##KIND##_FIRST will be the low boundary
32 BDESC_END (KIND, NEXT_KIND)
33 -- marks the end of bdesc_##kind, defines
34 IX86_BUILTIN__BDESC_##KIND##_LAST to be
35 IX86_BUILTIN__BDESC_##NEXT_KIND##_FIRST - 1. */
36
